<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَو تَزْوِيجهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَا بُد من ذكر الْمَفْعُول فِي الْجَانِبَيْنِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَيصِح تَقْدِيم لفظ الزَّوْج على<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لفظ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>الْوَلِيّ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَيَقُول الزَّوْج زَوْجَتي ابْنَتك فَيَقُول الْوَلِيّ زوجتكها<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ولايصح<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عقد النِّكَاح<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِلَّا بِلَفْظ التَّزْوِيج أَو الانكاح<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>دون الْهِبَة أَو التَّمْلِيك<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيصِح بالعجمية<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وان أحسن الْعَرَبيَّة<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فِي الْأَصَح<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَمُقَابِله لَا يَصح اعْتِبَارا بِاللَّفْظِ الْوَارِد فَيجب الصَّبْر إِلَى أَن يتعلمه وَمحل الْخلاف إِذا فهم كل من الْعَاقِدين كَلَام الآخر والا فَلَا يَصح<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لَا بكناية قطعا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فِي الصِّيغَة كأحللتك ابْنَتي أما فِي الْمَعْقُود عَلَيْهِ كزوجتك بِنْتي ونويا مُعينَة فانه يَصح<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلَو قَالَ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>الْوَلِيّ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>زَوجتك فَقَالَ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>الزَّوْج<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>قبلت<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَاقْتصر عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>لم ينْعَقد على الْمَذْهَب<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَفِي قَول ينْعَقد بذلك<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَلَو قَالَ زَوجنِي<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>بنتك الخ<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>فَقَالَ<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>الْوَلِيّ لَهُ<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>زَوجتك<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>إِلَى آخِره<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>أَو قَالَ الْوَلِيّ تزَوجهَا<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>أَي ابْنَتي<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>فَقَالَ تزوجت<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>الخ<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>صَحَّ<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>النِّكَاح وان لم يقبل الزَّوْج بعد ذَلِك<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>وَلَا يَصح تَعْلِيقه<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>كاذا طلعت الشَّمْس فقد زَوجتك ابْنَتي<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>وَلَو بشر بِولد فَقَالَ<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>لآخر<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>ان كَانَ انثى فقد زوجتكها أَو قَالَ ان كَانَت بِنْتي طلقت واعتدت فقد زوجتكها<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>وَكَانَت أَذِنت لأَبِيهَا فِي زواجها<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>فَالْمَذْهَب بُطْلَانه<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span>أَي النِّكَاح فِي الصُّور الْمَذْكُورَة<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>وَلَا<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>يَصح<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span>توقيته<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>أَي النِّكَاح بِمدَّة مَعْلُومَة أَو مَجْهُولَة<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>وَلَا<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>يَصح<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
